Various exercises for my cryptography course, coded in C++.
rc4: Implementation of the RC4 cipher.
otp: Implementation of the one time pad encryption technique.
ex2: Code for examining the avalanche effect in AES and Camellia ciphers. Uses the OpenSSL library.
ex3: Code for cracking the Vigenere cipher.
